Package com.ultreon.mods.lib.core.silentlib.data

Class ExtendedShapedRecipeBuilder

java.lang.Object
com.ultreon.mods.lib.core.silentlib.data.ExtendedShapedRecipeBuilder
@Deprecated public class ExtendedShapedRecipeBuilder extends Object
Deprecated.
Very similar to ShapedRecipeBuilder, but with a couple of changes. Intended to generate ExtendedShapedRecipes. Extra data can be quickly added to serialization by either calling addExtraData(Consumer) or extending this class and overriding serializeExtra(JsonObject).

If an advancement criterion is not added, no advancement is generated, instead of throwing an exception.
